verbose_text: In the weaned piglets, RV infusion, to different degrees, increased the mRNA expressions of NF-kappaB, TLR3, RIG-I, MDA5, TRIF, TRAF3, NEMO, TAK1, IRF3, MAVS, pBD2, and pBD3 in the ileum and/or mesenteric lymph nodes (P < 0.05 or P < 0.10, Table XREF_TABLE).
evidence: expressions of NF-kappaB, TLR3, RIG-I, MDA5, TRIF, TRAF3, NEMO, TAK1, IRF3, MAVS
